RACE.FOOTNOTES: UNCAPTURED DREAM stalked the pace along the inside, challenged for the lead entering the stretch, dueled briefly and drew off. MASQUERADE BALL raced mid pack, put in a steady effort and was along for show. STOLICH was off a step slowly, raced inside in a steady effort and gained late to improve position. I'M YOUR CAPTAIN set the pace, responded when challenged to duel, gave way and dropped back. SUNDAY MISCHIEF stalked the pace to the turn, fell back, went five wide entering the stretch, lacked a rally and stopped.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: Peach of It H. HAWTHORNE RACE 4 1 1/16M Dirt CR: 100. Stakes Purse 75000. FOR FILLIES AND MARES, THREE-YEARS-OLD AND UPWARD. ILLINOIS REGISTERED CONCEIVED AND/OR FOALED.
